{"article_id":"KtJv7rHSMBidXhXc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Hours after President Donald Trump said","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"his lawyer Rudy Giuliani did not have \" his facts straight , \"","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"the former New York mayor issued a statement on Friday","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"$ 130,000 in hush money","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"paid to an adult-film star before the 2016 election","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"was not an election law violation .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Giuliani on Thursday had connected the payment to Stormy Daniels by the president ' s personal lawyer , Michael Cohen ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to keep quiet about a 2006 sexual encounter","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"she said","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"she had with Trump to the election ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"remarks","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that raised the possibility","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that the transaction violated federal election law .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" There is no campaign violation .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The payment was made","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"to resolve a personal and false allegation","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"in order to protect the President ' s family .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"It would have been done in any event ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"whether he was a candidate or not , \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Giuliani said in a brief statement","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"\" intended to clarify the views","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"I expressed over the past few days . \"","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Giuliani in a TV interview on Thursday wondered","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"what would have happened","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"if Daniels ' claim of an affair had come up in a debate between Trump and his Democratic opponent , Hillary Clinton ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"adding ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"\" Cohen made it go away .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"He did his job . \"","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"In comments to reporters at the White House","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"before boarding a helicopter ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Trump seemed to undercut Giuliani , a former federal prosecutor","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"who the president recently hired","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to represent him .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Giuliani conducted a series of news media interviews this week","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that only intensified the controversy","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"involving Daniels ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"whose real name is Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and other matters .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" Rudy is a great guy ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"but he just started a day ago .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"But he really has his heart into it .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"He ' s working hard .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"He ' s learning the subject matter , \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" He ' ll get his facts straight , \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Trump added ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"though he did not specify the statements by Giuliani ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"who joined the president ' s legal team on April 19 ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"to which he was referring .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Giuliani late on Wednesday revealed","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that Trump had repaid Cohen for the $ 130,000","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the lawyer had provided to Daniels .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Trump previously had denied knowing about the payment .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump gestures","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"before boarding Marine One","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"to travel to Texas from the South Lawn of the White House in Washington , U.S. , May 4 , 2018 .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"/Matej Leskovsek","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"The next morning , Trump said on Twitter","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"that Cohen was paid back through a monthly retainer , not campaign funds ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"to stop Daniels ' \" false and extortionist accusations . \"","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Asked about the matter on Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"without explicitly mentioning Giuliani ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that \" virtually everything said","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"has been said incorrectly ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and it ' s been said wrong ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"or it ' s been covered wrong by the press . \"","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"In his statement on Friday , Giuliani said ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" My references to timing were not describing my understanding of the President ' s knowledge ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"but instead , my understanding of these matters , \"","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"but did not provide specifics .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Giuliani in an appearance on Fox News on Wednesday had said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Trump fired James Comey as FBI director last year","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"because Comey declined to state publicly","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that Trump was not at the time a target of the agency ' s investigation into Russia ' s role in the election .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Critics have pointed to Comey ' s firing as evidence of obstruction of justice by Trump .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"In his Friday statement , Giuliani said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"it was \" undisputed \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that Trump had the constitutional power","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"to fire Comey","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and that doing so has turned out to be \" plainly in the best interests of our nation . \"","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"The Republican president ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"facing legal troubles on several fronts ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"also indicated","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"he would be willing to be interviewed in Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"but only if he knew","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"he would be treated fairly .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Mueller is probing potential collusion between the Trump campaign and Russia","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and whether the president has unlawfully sought to obstruct the investigation .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"\" Nobody wants to speak more than me ...","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"because we ' ve done nothing wrong , \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"\" I have to find","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"that we ' re going to be treated fairly ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"because everybody sees it now ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"and it is a pure witch hunt , \"","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Trump added ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"while incorrectly saying","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that Mueller , a Republican former FBI director , has a \" group of investigators","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that are all Democrats . \"","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"\" If I thought","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"it was fair ,","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"I would override my lawyer , \"","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Trump added .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"During a pretrial hearing in Virginia on Mueller ' s charges against Trump ' s former campaign chairman , Paul Manafort , U.S. District Judge T.S . Ellis III openly questioned","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"whether the special counsel had exceeded his prosecutorial powers","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"by bringing the case .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":217,"left":0,"right":216,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":216,"left":162,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":137,"right":161,"rela